corporate  siebert cisneros shank  co llc submit corporate in november  siebert cisneros shank acquired siebert capital markets this acquisition expanded siebert cisneros shank’s product and service offerings from its focus on municipals to include corporate investment banking both debt  equity corporate share repurchase and equity execution debt and equity capital marketscorporate share repurchasedebt and equity capital marketsdebt and equity capital markets siebert cisneros shank’s mission is to provide a unique comprehensive and valueadded platform for our clients’ investment banking needs the professionals on our team have on average over  years of experience on wall street we provide a fully integrated origination sales trading and distribution platform for an extensive array of products including corporate agency preferred moneymarket instruments equity and securitized products the capital markets group has participated in over  trillion of both global corporate bond and equity transactions since  for a wide variety of companies issuer coverage extends across a range of automotive financial industrial and utility clients siebert cisneros shank has both middle market institutional and retail distribution this retail distribution consists of small and high net worth investors that have consistently generated substantial demand on our retailtargeted products—ipos followons and preferred stock offerings our institutional client base consists of primarily tier  and middle market accounts which invest in a variety of asset classes these clients consist of mutual fund complexes asset managers insurance companies trust companies and public pension systems the strength of siebert cisneros shank’s institutional distribution platform lies in its coverage of nd and rd tier accounts which are sometimes underserved by the larger investment banks allowing us to bring significant added value to our clients’ transactions corporate share repurchasecorporate share repurchase siebert brandford shank’s capital markets group has a strong track record and extensive experience working with companies in executing their corporate share repurchase programs over the past ten years we have helped repurchase over  million shares representing  billion in principal amount for a variety of fortunerated companies our team has distinguished itself in this product offering demonstrating that small firms can compete effectively the capital markets group was awarded “best share repurchase agent” for  years in a row by walmart stores inc servicesinvestment banking  underwritingpublic financecorporatesales  tradingfinancial advisory servicesresearch  market analyses   siebert cisneros shank  co llc  member finra and sipc home services   investment banking  underwriting public finance corporate sales  trading financial advisory services research  market analyses about   about our firm our team community involvement experience   sector experience airports  seaports corporates education general obligation statelevel transportation water  sewer other experience case studies rankings news  media contact us   locations careers request info home  siebert cisneros shank  co llc submit siebert cisneros shank serves new york city municipal water finance authority as senior manager on  million current refunding learn more the  million series a go bonds price at the tightest spreads ever achieved in the history of the district of columbia’s go credit learn more siebert cisneros shank achieves attractive pricing results for chicago’s  million wastewater transmission revenue bonds learn more in april  fort bend isd became the first texas school district to issue green bonds learn more series a revenue bonds are dasnys fourth financing solely secured by the university systems dormitory facilities revenue program learn more atlanta achieves approximately  million of pv savings on this  million refunding in april  learn more third successfully seniormanaged deal for san antoni